Title: ntp: Check_MK Discovery crash "invalid literal for int() with base 10: 'st'"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1616850595
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p2

The ntp check caused a Check_MK Discovery service crash with the error message
"ValueError (invalid literal for int() with base 10: 'st')". This has been
fixed.
